page.title: 03HANNAH'S DAY IN HONLEY (2)
page.content: 14.14-I went to the toilet and then went to play out. 17.20-I had a salad tea. 17.30-Had a further session of playing out; "Making Dens". 19.30-I came indoors and watched some television. 20.12-Bathtime! Naturally I undressed before leaping into the bath! 20.25-On climbing out of the bath, I dried myself and put on my pyjamas. 20.32-I ate some chips whilst watching television. 21.26-My teeth were brushed and I went to the toilet. 21.30-Bedtime! An exhausting Saturday had come to a close.
